font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，个人促成了网络模型研究的消亡，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">并</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">标志着连接主义研究第一阶段的结束。</span></span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">由</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">马文</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·明斯基和西摩·帕普特领导</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">了</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一场运动，旨在</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">批评</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经网络研究，并将神经网络研究资金转移到</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“人工智能”领域。这场运动</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">始于</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一份技术手稿</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">明斯基和帕普特及其盟友</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">之间</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">传阅</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。该手稿后来经过进一步的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">润色、</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">提炼和扩充，于</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1969</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年由明斯基和帕普特出版，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">书名</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">为《</span></span><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px;">Perceptrons</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">感知</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">机</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）》（</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参考资料</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">[1]</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">此书出版后，充满争议。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在布朗克斯理工高中（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">Bronx High School of Science</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">），马文·明斯基</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">罗森布拉特</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是同学。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">60</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">明斯基</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">曾经</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">对罗森布拉特的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">感知机进行过研究和完善，但</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">他对罗森布拉特的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">工作</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">深表怀疑。在会议上，罗森布拉特和明斯基公开</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">辩论</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">了感知机的可行性，他们的同事和学生惊讶地看着。罗森布拉特的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">目标</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是让机器识别</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">物体</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。而</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这在</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">60</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年后</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">才</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">最终能够做到的。问题是，罗森布拉特的感知机只有一层，而现代神经网络有数百层。当时，罗森布拉特不知道如何训练多层网络。但事后看来，罗森布拉特的算法仍然是我们今天如何训练深层网络的基础。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">在《感知机》一书中，明斯基和帕普特认为，网络研究计划存在一些基本问题。他们认为有一些任务，例如计算连通性的拓扑函数和奇偶性的计算，罗森布拉特的感知机无法解决。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">特别是</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">感知机不能学习</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">计算</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“异或（</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">XOR</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">）”的逻辑函数。明斯基和帕普特的分析结果使他们得出这样的结论：尽管感知机的研究“有趣”，但最终感知机及其可能的扩展，是一个</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">没有前途</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的研究方向。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">明斯基在他的《感知</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">机</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">》一书中指出，当前研究神经网络的模型是不可能的，计算时间如果不是无限的话，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">也是</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">漫长的，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">是一个主要问题。《感知</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">机》一书</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">介绍</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">了</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">计算几何，第二年，明斯基获得了</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">A.M.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">图灵奖——计算机的最高荣誉，他</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">帕普特</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">并</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">成为新的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">成立的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">麻省理工学院人工智能实验室的联合主任。</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">70</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代初出版了一个手写的修订版和增补版，</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1987</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年又出版了一个扩充版，其中有一章专门用来反驳</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">80</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代对它的批评。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">明斯基和西摩</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">·派珀特</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">《感知机》这本书抨击了罗森布拉特的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">工作</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">，并从本质上决定了它的命运，全球主要大学对神经网络相关研究进行了十多年的非正式</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“冻结”，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">同时，</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">导致了所谓的</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“ </span><span style="font-family: Arial;">AI </span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">寒冬</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">”。</span></span></p><p style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left; text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">罗森布拉特没有活过人工智能的</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">寒冬</span></span><span style="color: #080E14; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">。</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">1971</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年，他</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">43</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">岁生日时，在切萨皮克湾驾驶一艘名为“希尔沃特”的单桅帆船时溺水身亡。</span></span></p><p style="-ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">【</span></span></strong><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">结语】</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">不管是否真的完全由于明斯基</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">“权威”武断的话，导致了神经网络研究的衰落，但，类似的事情在科技界并不少见。不过，明斯基的《感知机》一书，是学术性的，尽管在</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">80</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代实践证明（在后面的博文中将讨论），他的结论过于仓促。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 28px; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">神经网络和人工智能，一荣俱荣</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">,</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一损俱损。人工智能第一个寒冬，是由于感知机的衰落引起的，后来人工智能的第二个寒冬，则是由专家系统市场崩溃引起的，连带了神经网络的衰落，而</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">21</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">世纪</span><span style="font-family: Arial;">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">年代深度学习的辉煌，也造就了人工智能的繁荣。</span></span></p><p style="-ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><strong><span style="color: #0000FF; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">参考资料：</span></span></strong></p><p style="-ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-autospace: ideograph-numeric;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">[1] Marvin Minsky and Seymour Papert. Perceptrons. An Introduction to Computational Geometry. M.I.T. Press, Cambridge, Mass., 1969</span></span></p><p> </p>                    <br><br>
